snippet.title: Su-25 Stormovik gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Su-25 Stormovik (aka stormovik: su-25 soviet attack fighter), Dos PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/su-25-stormovik/5773/
Exploring the interface and flying around in this combat flight simulator.

Recorded with original sound.
